        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="crash-content" value="When a phase is marked &lt;b&gt;running&lt;/b&gt; on startup:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. Read PID from phase_state.json&lt;br&gt;2. &lt;code&gt;os.kill(pid, 0)&lt;/code&gt; — check if process alive&lt;br&gt;3. If &lt;b&gt;dead&lt;/b&gt;: mark as &lt;b&gt;failed&lt;/b&gt; (&quot;Process terminated unexpectedly&quot;)&lt;br&gt;4. If &lt;b&gt;alive&lt;/b&gt; but older than 1 hour: mark as &lt;b&gt;failed&lt;/b&gt; (stale)&lt;br&gt;5. If &lt;b&gt;alive&lt;/b&gt; and recent: keep as &lt;b&gt;running&lt;/b&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
